{"TopicId":196129,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Crew Hatch Part","CreatedByName":"JMBuilder","CreatedById":30493,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-06T00:42:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JMBuilder","CreatedById":30493,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-06T00:42:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably the most basic yet most quality-of-life-oriented part I\u0027ve ever suggested.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s as simple as a spare hatch that would provide Kerbals with an alternative route to take when exiting or boarding vessels.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd... that\u0027s pretty much it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Qubyte","CreatedById":206519,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-06T02:22:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat would be a nice addition, depending on it\u0027s exact dimensions and mechanics. Something else to add would be the ability to EVA through a hatch on a different crewed part. I hate juggling kerbals via the current UI just so that I can get my engineer out to fix some tires or something like that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JMBuilder","CreatedById":30493,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-06T02:30:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m wanting one to put in cargo bays. An upside-down Mk2 cargo bay is perfect for crew access to cargo and a deployable ladder. I just need that darn hatch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-06T12:17:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere *are* a couple of small part mods that have attachable hatches/airlocks:\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022136290\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7729053873\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/144599-wip-add-on-airlocks/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:209px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022133496\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1145235636\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/151443-1xx-mk1-cabin-hatch-v100-26-april-2020/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:209px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs well as this small, simple plugin that adds hatch functionality to stock docking ports:\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002280345\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7691544419\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/190983-19x-all-aboard-1011-19022020-allowing-kerbals-to-board-through-docking-ports-since-2020/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:209px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, I bleieve the Making History DLC contains a small inflatable airlock part... vOv\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-06T12:18:29Z\u0022 title=\u002208/06/2020 12:18  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 6, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JMBuilder","CreatedById":30493,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-06T19:30:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll cool and good, but for as long as this game is still receiving updates, I\u0027d like to go full stock. If and when they stop, I\u0027ll be modding the snot out of it.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-06T20:26:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also asked for this a while back, but no luck so far. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}